Construction Associate 1-2PQE, Dubai
Construction Associate 1-2PQE, Dubai
Location:  --Dubai
This well-established international law firm has one of the region’s largest and most highly regarded construction practices. The firm is now seeking to recruit a construction associate to join the team in Dubai.
The ideal candidate will be 1-2PQE and have mixed front and back end construction experience gained at a reputable law firm with a strong presence in the field of mainstream construction. Although candidates with either purely contentious or non-contentious experience will also be considered. Regional experience whilst preferable is not mandatory. You will be driven, enthusiastic and a team player with a genuine interest in marketing and relationship building.
For further details, candidates fulfilling the above criteria are invited to send their CV in complete confidence to
